title: Bug 29769Ajde does not support new AspectJ 1.1 compiler options
description: Bug 29769Ajde does not support new AspectJ 1.1 compiler options These need to be added to the interface, any oldor renamed options deprecated, and then the correct processing needs to happenwithin Ajde to pass these options to the compiler.This enhancement is needed by the various IDE projects for there AspectJ 1.1support.
OB: The org.aspectj.ajde.BuildOptionsAdapter interface does not yet support the newAspectJ 1.1 compiler options.
